istening. Thing do taste on we manor.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </li> -->\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6\">\n            <div class=\"experience wow fadeInRight\" data-wow-delay=\"0.6s\">\n              <ul class=\"timeline\">\n                <li>\n                  <i class=\"icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                  <h2 class=\"timelin-title\">Experience</h2>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <div class=\"content-text\">\n                    <h3 class=\"line-title\">Junior Software Engineer </h3>\n                    <span>September 2019 - December 2019</span>\n                    <p class=\"line-text\">Developing React Single Page Application and Components for\n                      marketing and lead generation websites (One Big Switch, FiftyUp\n                      Club and 9 Saver) and testing them using React Testing Library and\n                      Jest Framework. I also developed the REST APIs using AWS Lambda\n                      (Node Js), DynamoDB and other Microservices. Moreover, I was also\n                      responsible for refactoring and developing the current AWS\n                      Infrastructure using cloudformation templates.</p>\n\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <div class=\"content-text\">\n                    <h3 class=\"line-title\">Front End Developer </h3>\n                    <span>March 2016 - December 2016</span>\n                    <p class=\"line-text\">I worked in the HR Domain, our entire effort was to develop a smart\n                      hiring platform that had candidate profiles sourced from various\n                      digital Footprints like LinkedIn, Github and about.me. I was\n                      responsible for developing the User Interaction and User Experience\n                      to facilitate a smooth hiring experience for the recruiters.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <div class=\"content-text\">\n                    <h3 class=\"line-title\">Intern Web Developer - Kiljir Consultancy LLP</h3>\n                    <span>Mar 2015 - Oct 2016</span>\n                    <p class=\"line-text\">I had been working on a Fintech company's website. The goal was to\n                      digitise the entire company's business process and to design a\n                      robust and user friendly User Experience. The project was\n                      developed using the Codeigniter (Php)/MySql for backend and\n                      Html/CSS3, Bootstrap for frontend.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Resume Section End -->\n\n    <!-- Portfolio Section -->\n    <section id=\"portfolios\" class=\"section-padding\">\n      <!-- Container Starts -->\n      <div class=\"container\">        \n        <h2 class=\"section-title wow flipInX\" data-wow-delay=\"0.4s\">My Portfolio</h2>\n        <div class=\"row\">          \n          <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n            <!-- Portfolio Controller/Buttons -->\n            <!-- <div class=\"controls text-center\">\n              <a class=\"filter active btn btn-common\" data-filter=\"all\">\n                All \n              </a>\n              <a class=\"filter btn btn-common\" data-filter=\".design\">\n                Design \n              </a>\n              <a class=\"filter btn btn-common\" data-filter=\".development\">\n                Development\n              </a>\n              <a class=\"filter btn btn-common\" data-filter=\".print\">\n                Print \n              </a>\n            </div> -->\n            <!-- Portfolio Controller/Buttons Ends-->\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- Portfolio Recent Projects -->\n          <div id=\"po